OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1779883867
OL,3,CFather's stark warning to parents
OL,4,Cafter sons death at Lincoln lake
OL,6,FTributes have been paid to 15-year-old
OL,7,FDeclan Sawyer who died after entering
OL,8,Fa lake in Lincoln.
OL,10,FEmergency services were called to the
OL,11,Farea at 2.30pm on Sunday 24 May,
OL,12,Ffollowing reports of a boy getting
OL,13,Finto trouble in the water.
OL,15,FAt 10.25pm on Sunday Lincolnshire
OL,16,FPolice confirmed that the body of
OL,17,FDeclan Sawyer had been recovered.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/6
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
