OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1779883867
OL,3,CFather's stark warning to parents
OL,4,Cafter sons death at Lincoln lake
OL,6,FIn a tribute, his father Carl
OL,7,Fdescribed him as "a funny and outgoing
OL,8,Fyoung man who loved fishing and
OL,9,Ffootball".
OL,11,FHe added: "He had a very cheeky smile
OL,12,Fand the personality to match. He was
OL,13,Fvery much loved by his friends and
OL,14,Ffamily, and will be missed dearly by
OL,15,Fmany.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/6
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
