PN,36603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1779883867
OL,3,CFather's stark warning to parents
OL,4,Cafter sons death at Lincoln lake
OL,6,F"With his tragic and unexpected
OL,7,Fpassing on Sunday 24th May at
OL,8,FSwanholme Lakes, we would like to
OL,9,Fraise awareness about children playing
OL,10,Fnear any rivers or lakes in the hot
OL,11,Fweather.
OL,13,F"Please can all parents, friends and
OL,14,Ffamily make their children aware of
OL,15,Fthe dangers surrounding water."
OL,17,FThe Priory Lincoln Academy school have
OL,18,Falso paid tribute to Declan stating
OL,19,Fthat the "entire Priory Lincoln
OL,20,Flearning community is grieving
OL,21,Falongside Declan's family and friends".
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/6
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
