SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1779883867
OL,3,CFather's stark warning to parents
OL,4,Cafter sons death at Lincoln lake
OL,6,FThe school added: "Declan was a valued
OL,7,Fmember of our academy and a loyal
OL,8,Ffriend to many students. His presence
OL,9,Fand character in our Academy will be
OL,10,Fsorely missed by staff and students
OL,11,Falike, and his absence will be felt
OL,12,Fprofoundly in the coming days, weeks
OL,13,Fand months ahead."
OL,15,FThe school have reassured parents that
OL,16,Fthey have pastoral teams, counsellors
OL,17,Fand trusted adults across the school
OL,18,Fto provide support for students.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/6
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
