PN,36605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1779883867
OL,3,CFather's stark warning to parents
OL,4,Cafter sons death at Lincoln lake
OL,6,FDeclan played on the U15 team at St
OL,7,FHelens football club in Lincoln. The
OL,8,Fclub described him as a "valued
OL,9,Fmember" of the team and added that
OL,10,Ftheir "thoughts and prayers are with
OL,11,FDeclan's family, friends, teammates,
OL,12,Fcoaches and everyone who knew and
OL,13,Floved him".
OL,15,FThe incident happened as extreme
OL,16,Fweather in the UK led to hottest day
OL,17,Fin May ever recorded, with
OL,18,Ftemperatures reaching 34.8C in parts
OL,19,Fof England on Monday.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G5/6
